OL,3,CPolice force mergers 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cbut 'challenging', former Kent chief
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FGovernment plans to merge county
OL,8,Fconstabularies into large regional
OL,9,Fpolice forces are "long overdue", a
OL,10,Fformer Kent chief constable has
OL,11,Fclaimed.
OL,13,FMichael Fuller, who led the force from
OL,14,F2004 to 2010, told ITV News that the
OL,15,Fcurrent force structure was
OL,16,F"indefensible" but warned that
OL,17,Fministers "shouldn't underestimate the
OL,18,Fscale of the challenge" involved in
OL,19,Fmergers.
