OL,3,CPolice force mergers 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cbut 'challenging', former Kent chief
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FThe government has proposed the number
OL,8,Fof forces in England and Wales be
OL,9,Fsignificantly reduced, with the new,
OL,10,Flarger forces divided into local areas
OL,11,Fcorresponding with cities, towns and
OL,12,Fboroughs.
OL,14,FMr Fuller, who was Britain's first
OL,15,Fblack chief constable, said: "These
OL,16,Freforms are long overdue. At the
OL,17,Fmoment, you've got 43 police forces.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/5
