OL,3,CPolice force mergers 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cbut 'challenging', former Kent chief
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,F"They all have different uniforms,
OL,8,Fdifferent police cars, different makes
OL,9,Fof police cars, different processes
OL,10,Fand systems for recording and
OL,11,Freporting crime. The whole system is
OL,12,Freally indefensible as it stands at
OL,13,Fthe moment."
OL,15,FBut the former chief constable
OL,16,Fcautioned that there was "a danger"
OL,17,Fthat the chief constable of larger,
OL,18,Fregional forces might become "more
OL,19,Fremote and distant" from the public
OL,20,Fthey serve.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/5
