OL,3,CPolice force mergers 'long overdue'
OL,4,Cbut 'challenging', former Kent chief
OL,5,Cclaims
OL,7,FMr Fuller added: "One of the things I
OL,8,Ffelt in Kent was a great ownership by
OL,9,Fthe local populace of their police
OL,10,Fforce. So, I think local identity
OL,11,Famongst police forces is important."
OL,13,FThe former police leader ` who was in
OL,14,Fpost when a previous Labour government
OL,15,Fproposed similar force amalgamations
OL,16,Fin the 2000s ` also warned about the
OL,17,Fcomplexity of any mergers.
OL,19,F"It's a huge undertaking and the scale
OL,20,Fof the challenge should not be
OL,21,Funderestimated by the Home Secretary."
